leopard-print pumps

05:43.232 --> 05:46.383
and a rack-tastic red dress
from Forever 21.

05:52.407 --> 05:53.941
And there's Amy,

05:53.943 --> 05:55.609
showing all kinds of ankle.

05:56.778 --> 06:00.614
